    ) external;

    /**
     * @dev Mints a Second Level Domain (SLD) with records.
     * Implements a ERC721Reciever check unlike mintSLD.
     * @param to address to mint the new SLD to.
     * @param tld id of parent token.
     * @param label SLD label to mint.
